"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1446, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9999993883163422, \"rank\": 5.883450311233089e-07, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999992492576, \"rank\": 7.507486900926873e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9921609950108916, \"rank\": 0.00790093944114583, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vieira has since reacted to her expulsion, filming a video and posting it on Instagram while passing through Portugal.\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1864, \"end\": 1873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6477186157358245e-22, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1896, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"score\": 0.9988609702905147, \"rank\": 0.0011220874279561411, \"text\": \"Portugal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimming star who was accused of \\\"misconduct\\\" stressed that she did nothing wrong and accused the COB of ignoring complaints of harassment.\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2009, \"end\": 2012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazilian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2803299521357795e-24, \"text\": \"COB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazilian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazilian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I left there and left my materials.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not know what to do.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My things are there [in the Olympic Village].\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.868236922875195e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I went to the airport in shorts,\\\" Vieira explained.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had to open my suitcase at the airport.\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am in Portugal.\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2266, \"end\": 2274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"score\": 0.9988609702905147, \"rank\": 0.0011220874279561411, \"text\": \"Portugal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to Recife and then to Sao Paulo.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2309, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\", \"score\": 0.9858779573453796, \"rank\": 0.012363781011925925, \"text\": \"Sao Paulo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am helpless.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had no access to anything.\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not been able to speak to anyone.\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They told me to contact the COB channels.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2440, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazilian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2803299521357795e-24, \"text\": \"COB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazilian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazilian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But how am I going to get in touch?\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have already filed a complaint of harassment, and nothing has been resolved, harassment within the team.\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  She continued: \\\"I will speak to my lawyers.\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I promise to tell everything.\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sad, nervous, but with peace of mind because I know who I am.\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know what my character and my nature are.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope to be able to defend Brazilian women's swimming with great pride.\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I ask for patience and thank you.\\\"\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3277, \"end\": 3290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4490972575722284e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3326, \"end\": 3339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4490972575722284e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"